Preprocess the data (list or env) to list.

Preprocess the data (list or env) to list.

data_preprocess(data)

Arguments

data
A list or an environment of objects.

Details

stop if no-name lists; duplicate names. stop if the objects given name is not found. remove NULL, non-numeric elements
